reviewText: Given as a gift. Recipient was thrilled and has watched it NUMEROUS times and still looks at it again. Tells all of his friends about it and his new friends just have to see it with him. Great movie for a skateboarder.
It's even dumber than the first one, just stay away
Great movie, Great sequel, fun for the whole family. Quite a few co-stars you would recognize
The dvd was great entertainment for Grandson and Father. They are both into Bikes and Boards. The 5 yearold Grandson loves it!
Andrea Barber is a great actress and she is a very beautiful cover girl model of a young lady in every way

THIS MOVIE WAS AMAZING!! Anything with my love, Full House's Kimmy Gibbler (Andrea Barber), is of course a masterpiece, but this went beyond my wildest expectations. It makes me aroused just seeing her face in this movie. Watch Skateboard Kid 2 because it is awesome!!
